text: Irina Birvagen (; born 24 July 1988) is a Kazakhstani former footballer who played as a forward. She has been a member of the Kazakhstan women's national team. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Kazakhstani women's footballers Category:Kazakhstan women's international footballers Category:CSHVSM-Kairat players
